UEFA Will Make Step on Turkish Soccer Match-Fixing at Draw, Sabah Says

-- B y   M a r k   B e n t l e y
-- 
2011-08-17T06:06:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-17/uefa-will-make-step-on-turkish-soccer-match-fixing-at-draw-sabah-says.html
UEFA  will make a step concerning
Turkish soccer teams embroiled in match-fixing allegations at a
draw for the  Champions League  on Aug. 25, Sabah reported.  UEFA is watching how Turkish authorities deal with the
allegations and the day of the draw will be “very important,”
UEFA vice president Senes Erzik said, according to the Istanbul-
based newspaper.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
